      <title>孩童隨身繫 AirTag，Skechers 鞋裡藏</title>
      <description>&lt;figure class="mb-module-gap"&gt;&lt;div class="mx-auto w-fit"&gt;&lt;img alt="孩童隨身繫 AirTag，Skechers 鞋裡藏" class="rounded-lg" loading="lazy" height="480" src="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Xge_x4Tk3Qmn1SEv0IBU3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-07/40542290-6dd6-11f0-afdf-88c5fe924341" width="854" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"&gt;&lt;figcaption class="text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere" style="max-width:854px"&gt;孩童隨身繫 AirTag，&lt;a class="link " href="https://tw.news.yahoo.com/tag/Skechers" data-i13n="sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link" data-ylk="slk:Skechers;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0"&gt;Skechers&lt;/a&gt; 鞋裡藏&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;手機、手錶、IM 軟體... 為追蹤小孩子的位置現代家長們可謂費盡了心思。而如今 Skechers 急人之所急，推出了名為 F&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.skechers.com/find-my-skechers/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:ind My Skechers;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;ind My Skechers&lt;/a&gt; 的特殊鞋款。如名稱所示，它的鞋跟內設有專門用於放置 AirTag 的凹槽，可幫助父母透過 Apple 的 Find My 網路隨時掌握孩童動向。相比之下，這種追蹤方式更為隱秘、無感。但挖空一塊的設計對鞋子耐用性、穿著舒適度有沒有影響？尚且需要市場的檢驗。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;blockquote class="mb-module-gap"&gt;&lt;div class="bg-dirty-seagull" style="padding-bottom:min(300px, 56%)"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;目前的 Find My Skechers 提供了 1 歲至 10 歲孩童的尺碼，但僅有一個款式，售價在 US$50 左右（不含 AirTag）。如果市場反響出色的話，Skechers 大可擴充產品線。而且除了小孩以外，失智老人也是一個很大的潛在市場。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;緊貼最新科技資訊、網購優惠，追隨 Yahoo Tech 各大社交平台！&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;🎉📱 Tech Facebook：&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;https://www.facebook.com/yahootechhk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;🎉📱 Tech Instagram：&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;https://www.instagram.com/yahootechhk/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;🎉📱 Tech WhatsApp 社羣：&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;https://chat.whatsapp.com/Dg3fiiyYf3yG2mgts4Mii8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;🎉📱 Tech WhatsApp 頻道：&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas" class="link "&gt;https://whatsapp.com/channel/0029Va91dmR545urVCpQwq2D&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class="mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave"&gt;🎉📱 Tech Telegram 頻道：&lt;a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://t.me/yahootechhk" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-ylk="slk:https://t.me/yahootec